{"lemma":"غَيْهَبُ","slug":"غَيْهَبُ","root":"غ.ه.ب","root_slug":"غ-ه-ب","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-ه-ب","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":3,"pos_tags":["noun","verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":6},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n32562"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8E%D9%8A%D9%92%D9%87%D9%8E%D8%A8%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"darkness, obscurity"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"intense black"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"intensely black, of peculiarly dark colour"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"inadvertent, heedless, inattentive, inconsiderate"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"inert, timid, dull"},{"pos":"verb","gloss":"to debilitate the sight with darkness"}]},"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n32562","headword_ar":"غَيْهَبٌ","root":"ghb","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Darkness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, A, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gayohabaAnN","text_ar":"غَيْهَبَانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (K:) pl. of the former"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gayaAhibu","text_ar":"غَيَاهِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S.) ―         -b2-  And A horse, and night,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intensely black:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) or, instead of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAll~ayoli","text_ar":"وَاللَّيْلِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the K, we may read"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"waAll~ayolu","text_ar":"وَاللَّيْلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; so that the meaning may be, a horse"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intensely black:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"agreeably with the A, in which this latter meaning [as well as the former] is assigned to the word; and it is added that one says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aHosanu mino bayaADi Alkawokabi fiY sawaAdi Algayohabi","text_ar":"اَحْسَنُ مِنْ بَيَاضِ الكَوْكَبِ فِى سَوَادِ الغَيْهَبِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"More beautiful than the whiteness of the star in the blackness of night"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (TA:) or it signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"intense blackness"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the night and of a camel and the like: you say"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamalN gayohabN","text_ar":"جَمَلٌ غَيْهَبٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a deep-black camel:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, TA:) and also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asowadu gayohabN","text_ar":"اَسْوَدُ غَيْهَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gayohamN","text_ar":"غَيْهَمٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (Lh, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rajulN gayohabN","text_ar":"رَجُلٌ غَيْهَبٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a black man;"},{"kind":"text","text":"likened to the darkness of night: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"layolN gayohabN","text_ar":"لَيْلٌ غَيْهَبٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a dark night:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, TA:) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"farasN A^adohamu gayohabN","text_ar":"فَرَسٌ اَدْهَمُ غَيْهَبٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a horse intensely black:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Sh, S, TA:) and it is said in “ the Book of Horses ” by A 'Obeyd that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adohamu","text_ar":"اَدْهَمُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gayohabiY~N","text_ar":"غَيْهَبِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies [a horse]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of the deepest black hue:"},{"kind":"text","text":"that the fem. is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gayohabapN","text_ar":"غَيْهَبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and the pl.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gayaAhibu","text_ar":"غَيَاهِبُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and that"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dajuwjiY~N","text_ar":"دَجُوجِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is less than"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gayohabN","text_ar":"غَيْهَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in blackness, signifying “ of a clear black hue. ” (TA.)       -A2-  Also, applied to a man,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Unmindful, negligent, inattentive, inadvertent, inconsiderate,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heedless:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"weak,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"timid:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) or (K, TA, but in the CK “ and, ”) a"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"heavy, troublesome"},{"kind":"text","text":"man: or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stupid, dull,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wanting in intelligence;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"inert,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wanting in vigour."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA.) And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Lacking ability to seek his blood-revenge,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"retaliation;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EayohabN","text_ar":"عَيْهَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ehb","text_ar":"عهب"},{"kind":"text","text":".)       -A3-  And A [garment of the kind called]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"kisaA='","text_ar":"كِسَا=ء"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having much wool; very woolly;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) as also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EayohabN","text_ar":"عَيْهَبٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A male ostrich."},{"kind":"text","text":"(R, TA.)"}],"source_refs":["K","TA","Lth","Lh","Sh","S"]}]}}